  dialogLines:
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Dunia berubah sangat cepat beriringan dengan teknologi
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Di jaman ini orang-orang lebih suka musik elektronik.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Akibatnya, musik tradisional Nusantara perlahan dilupakan.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Tidak ada lagi suara angklung, totobuang, atau tifa.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Alat musik dan musik tradisional ditinggalkan begitu saja.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Bahkan banyak orang yang tidak mengenalnya lagi.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f0a948ad8060985438b8e87424ddfe0e, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Karena budaya mulai hilang, muncul energi misterius bernama...
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1f90751c80e12b9499bd9b35eafc9c32, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: '"NOISE"'
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1f90751c80e12b9499bd9b35eafc9c32, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Noise membuat manusia melupakan harmoni musik tradisional.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1f90751c80e12b9499bd9b35eafc9c32, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Semakin kuat Noise, semakin banyak budaya yang menghilang.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98128b313f6718b468e3a7bfcba3a270, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Di sebuah kota kecil...
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98128b313f6718b468e3a7bfcba3a270, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 428ee6664c472034a90efe1ac93139c0, type: 3}
    dialogText: Seorang mahasiswa bernama Aditya Prakasa (Aksa) sedang membersihkan
      gudang di rumah peninggalan kakeknya.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98128b313f6718b468e3a7bfcba3a270, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f767207bafc60a04a8793df135644b91, type: 3}
    dialogText: Disana ia menemukan sebuah kotak tua, karena penasaran Aksa pun membukanya.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98128b313f6718b468e3a7bfcba3a270, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 21de816aa8ae34043a5c97738347ede4, type: 3}
    dialogText: Saat membuka kotak itu, ia menemukan alat musik misterius.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98128b313f6718b468e3a7bfcba3a270, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f767207bafc60a04a8793df135644b91, type: 3}
    dialogText: "Ketika disentuh\u2014"
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e0762ba225fa88c48881dae2dfcce2d6, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: WHOOOOOSHH!!
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e0762ba225fa88c48881dae2dfcce2d6, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Cahaya memenuhi ruangan.
  - speakerName: 
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e0762ba225fa88c48881dae2dfcce2d6, type: 3}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    dialogText: Dan sejak malam itu, perjalanan Aksa dimulai.
  typingSpeed: 0.03
  nextSceneName: GameIntroScene
